{"title":"岩上青松——献给朝鲜的老大娘","authors":["戈壁舟"],"dates":[{"year":1954,"month":1,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩上青松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给朝鲜的老大娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戈壁舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有个老大娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住在前线上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人成天在打炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰塌她的房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼儿不离江河水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘绝不离家乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志愿军帮她挖地洞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘住着倒安康。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"媳妇大儿从军去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二儿年小在身旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉死在敌刀下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘埋头生产忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮弹打烂她麦苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮弹翻掉她谷秧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮弹埋了她黄豆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮弹打倒她高粱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地里还落大炸弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸弹坑象大池塘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘不哼气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸过马上就种上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看那岩上的青松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石缝里面长得壮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕投弹大炮轰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面有咱志愿军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜墙铁壁永不破，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她在这里生了根。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半夜睡不着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来点燃灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄豆泡好喂磨眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会磨了一大盆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作好豆腐叫儿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看天快明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母子抬着豆腐桶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒着炮火送前线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天亮敌打“起床炮”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大路小路都轰断。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮弹落的近，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子腿直闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她叫儿子不要怕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志愿军生活有困难！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火线没菜吃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光吃盐水饭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子有了劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲走的欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲过炮烟去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲过封锁线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豆腐送到阵地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士围着老大娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知怎说好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把她举的那样高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要又不行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只说不敢再来到；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千说万说都不听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔天老大娘又来了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这天天刚亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有启明星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四山还模糊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路上来了人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“起床炮”飞来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士直担心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮烟冲天起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人穿炮烟行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这下看清楚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子和母亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都叫头低些，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都叫快前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到三岔路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是杀人坑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手都捏出汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌炮又轰鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似落心上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士心好紧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟散人还在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照样慢慢行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过了危险地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里都高兴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知敌炮又追来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见炮烟不见人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士发急出阵地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见儿子见母亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人手提豆腐桶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照样急急在前进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士拥到她跟前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘脸色好阴沉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子炸死在路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮烟过去看的清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的战士流了泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的眼里冒火星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘眼里没泪水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有仇和恨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往日豆腐吃的香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天豆腐没人尝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天不说话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚上躺着想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千想万想没办法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样安慰老大娘？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜半来了攻击令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要夺对面那山岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是报仇好时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀敌安慰老大娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂好手榴弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端好冲锋枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄一怒冲上山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗插在敌阵上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人阵地满敌尸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼看就要东方亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘若能亲眼见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄心里才舒畅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘今天不会来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘在家多悲伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都想派人去看看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利消息都带上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天刚麻麻亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“起床炮”又响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山阵地不见人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有哨兵在张望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨兵回头看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小山路通后方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗颗炮弹落路边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色烟尘盖白霜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一股炮烟飞开去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么又见老大娘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘照样送豆腐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手提木桶有力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山青松迎风舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘白发随风扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全体英雄出阵地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄泪眼风吹凉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五三年十二月十九日于朝鲜前线松林小屋）（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗地插图"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}